  "Description": {
    "English": "A destructive <span class=\"name name-technology\">starship projectile launcher</span>, the weapons system of choice for the interstellar trader and pirate alike.<br><br>Use <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> to change weapon mode. Press <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> to fire.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种毁灭性的<span class=\"name name-technology\">飞船射弹发射器，</span>星际商人和海盗使用的武器系统。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>变更武器模式。按下<span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span>发射。",
    "TencentChinese": "该武器破坏力很强，适合用来快速击沉敌方飞船。<br><br>按 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 激活。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種極具破壞性的<span class=\"name name-technology\">太空船射彈發射器</span>，星際商人和海盜的首選武器系統。<br><br>使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> 即可切換武器模式。按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 即可開火。"
  },
  "Teach": true,
  "HintStart": "",
  "HintEnd": {
    "English": "Switch Weapon Mode by pressing <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPCYCLEWEAPON</span><br>Fire Weapons with <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span>",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "按 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPCYCLEWEAPON</span> 切换武器模式<br>按 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 用武器开火",
    "TraditionalChinese": "按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPCYCLEWEAPON</span> 切換武器模式<br>按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 發射武器"
  },
